a&#3; particularly&#3; important&#3; effect&#3; on&#3; the&#3; way&#3; schools&#3; are&#3; managed&#3; (Bloom&#3; et&#3; al.&#3; 2014).&#3;&#3; The&#3; autonomous&#3;
government&#3;schools&#3;garnered&#3;significantly&#3;higher&#3;management&#3;scores&#3;than&#3;public&#3;and&#3;private&#3;schools&#3;and&#3;
