Policy&#3;Goal&#3;One:&#3;Level&#3;of&#3;Autonomy&#3;in&#3;the&#3;Planning&#3;and&#3;Management&#3;of&#3;the&#3;School&#3;Budget&#3;
&#3;
This&#3; policy&#3; goal&#3; focuses&#3; on&#3; the&#3; degree&#3; of&#3; autonomy&#3; that&#3; schools&#3; have&#3; in&#3; planning&#3; and&#3; managing&#3; their&#3;
