&#3;
There&#3; are&#3; several&#3; ways&#3; for&#3; funds&#3; to&#3; be&#3; transferred&#3; to&#3; schools.&#3;&#3; They&#3; include:&#3;&#3; central&#3; allocation&#3; to&#3; local&#3;
