1D.&#3; Legal&#3; authority&#3; to&#3; raise&#3; additional&#3; funds&#3; for&#3; the&#3; school.&#3; &#3; Greater&#3; community&#3; and&#3; parental&#3;
involvement&#3; in&#3; school&#3; affairs&#3; can&#3; sometimes&#3; lead&#3; to&#3; the&#3; school&#3; receiving&#3; more&#3; private&#3; donations&#3; and&#3;
