1E.&#3; Collaborative&#3; Budget&#3; Planning&#3; and&#3; Preparation.&#3; &#3; Parent&#3; collaboration&#3; in&#3; budget&#3; planning&#3; and&#3;
preparation&#3;has&#3;been&#3;recognized&#3;as&#3;a&#3;positive&#3;influence&#3;on&#3;transparency&#3;and&#3;accountability&#3;in&#3;the&#3;budget&#3;
