3A&#3; &&#3; B.&#3; Participation&#3; of&#3; the&#3; school&#3; council&#3; in&#3; budget&#3; preparation&#3; and&#3; financial&#3; oversight.&#3; The&#3;
participation&#3; of&#3; the&#3; school&#3; council&#3; in&#3; school&#3; finances&#3; has&#3; several&#3; links&#3; to&#3; autonomy&#3; and&#3; accountability.&#3;&#3;
