chances&#3; of&#3; higher&#3; student&#3; pass&#3; rates&#3; (Mulindwa,&#3; Habyarimana,&#3; and&#3; Bunjo&#3; 2013).&#3; &#3; In&#3; Mexicoâ€™s&#3; Quality&#3;
Schools&#3; Program&#3; (PEC),&#3; Parent&#3; Councils&#3; (Padres&#3; de&#3; Familia)&#3; are&#3; active&#3; in&#3; the&#3; preparation&#3; of&#3; the&#3; school&#3;
budget.&#3; They&#3; prepare&#3; a&#3; plan&#3; for&#3; improving&#3; the&#3; schoolâ€™s&#3; quality&#3; and&#3; then&#3; receive&#3; a&#3; fiveÍ²year&#3; grant&#3; to&#3;
implement&#3;the&#3;activities&#3;based&#3;on&#3;the&#3;school&#3;plan.&#3;The&#3;PEC&#3;grant&#3;is&#3;allocated&#3;to&#3;different&#3;areas&#3;of&#3;school&#3;
