&#12;failure,&#3; and&#3; repetition&#3; rates&#3; (Skoufias&#3; and&#3; Shapiro,&#3; 2006).&#3; Financial&#3; oversight&#3; is&#3; also&#3; a&#3; common&#3; function&#3;
of&#3;school&#3;councils&#3;and&#3;is&#3;an&#3;important&#3;component&#3;for&#3;accountability&#3;and&#3;efficiency.&#3;Financial&#3;oversight&#3;by&#3;
