3C.&#3; Participation&#3; of&#3; the&#3; school&#3; council&#3; in&#3; personnel&#3; oversight.&#3; Personnel&#3; oversight&#3; is&#3; one&#3; of&#3; the&#3; key&#3;
authorities&#3;that&#3;school&#3;councils&#3;can&#3;use&#3;to&#3;hold&#3;teachers&#3;accountable.&#3;&#3;It&#3;may&#3;include&#3;paying&#3;staff&#3;salaries,&#3;
