power&#3; in&#3; favor&#3; of&#3; parents&#3; and&#3; the&#3; school.&#3;&#3; Thus,&#3; necessary&#3; measures&#3; should&#3; be&#3; taken&#3; to&#3; deal&#3; with&#3; the&#3;
