3D.&#3;Participation&#3;of&#3;the&#3;school&#3;council&#3;in&#3;school&#3;activities.&#3;One&#3;of&#3;the&#3;core&#3;objectives&#3;of&#3;decentralization&#3;
is&#3;to&#3;expand&#3;the&#3;involvement&#3;of&#3;actors&#3;who&#3;do&#3;not&#3;belong&#3;to&#3;the&#3;community&#3;of&#3;education&#3;professionals,&#3;
