&#3;
In&#3; Liberia,&#3; a&#3; randomized&#3; controlled&#3; trial&#3; was&#3; conducted&#3; in&#3; 180&#3; schools&#3; where&#3; a&#3; group&#3; of&#3; 60&#3; schools&#3;
