&#3;
&#12;student&#3;achievement&#3;levels&#3;while&#3;an&#3;annual&#3;assessment&#3;or&#3;those&#3;provided&#3;with&#3;a&#3;regular&#3;frequency&#3;allows&#3;
for&#3; the&#3; possibility&#3; of&#3; monitoring&#3; trends&#3; in&#3; achievement&#3; and&#3; learning&#3; levels&#3; over&#3; time.&#3; &#3; Additionally,&#3;
