the&#3; budgetary&#3; autonomy&#3; decentralized&#3; to&#3; communes.&#3;&#3;&#3; The&#3; study&#3; confirmed&#3; that&#3; one&#3; of&#3; the&#3; key&#3; policy&#3;
messages&#3; of&#3; the&#3; SABERÍ²SAA&#3; framework,&#3; the&#3; 3&#3; As&#3; working&#3; together&#3; in&#3; balance&#3; enable&#3; better&#3; learning&#3;
