good&#3; results&#3; is&#3; tied&#3; to&#3; adequate&#3; funding&#3; and&#3; management&#3; of&#3; those&#3; funds.&#3;&#3; As&#3; academic&#3; accountability&#3;
becomes&#3; more&#3; routine,&#3; financial&#3; support&#3; can&#3; be&#3; forthcoming.&#3; Participation&#3; of&#3; the&#3; school&#3; council&#3; in&#3; the&#3;
